cause_text: And I jump in the air and he dodges out the way and I bring the spear down and wedges itself into the floor. And then I use it to spin myself around and kick him in the chest, which has been interpreted by fans as a demonstration of my hidden talent at pole dancing.
Yes, thank you for saving me.
We never picture of you in rehearsals where it doesn't look like it's going that well.
emotion_text: That's the best thing I've ever seen.
